Acqiris Software 2.15 (Jan 11, 2006)
=====================

AcqirisDemo: Uses version 3.6.1.3

- Added Load/Save options for gate definitions (AP240 SSR + AdvTDC)
- Added InterpolatedPeak feature for single peak and histograms (AP240 SSR +
AdvTDC)
